---
title: Golden Cauliflower & Lentil-Couscous with Yoghurt & Toasted Almonds
description: This is a bowl of pure plant-powered heaven. Curry-spiced cauliflower, roasted to crispy perfection sits atop a bed of fluffy couscous and flavourful lentils. A crunchy cucumber salad and a dollop of creamy yoghurt take it to the next level - fresh, hearty and oh-so-satisfying!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
